abstract: Indian police are searching for two officers in charge of patrolling village in Budaun district of Uttar Pradesh after a 14-year-old girl accuses them of raping her.
lead_paragraph: The two officers, who were in charge of patrolling the girl’s village, were suspended and are now missing, according a police official.

byline.original: By HARI KUMAR and NIDA NAJAR

headline.main: Indian Officials Seek 2 Police Officers Accused of Raping Girl, 14
